name: T'doshok Hunting Vow
Lore: 'Rek guza kias n''ek kriesuk zief. Rek res fesruk T''doshok kulesuk luk g''razzurg koref selukra fes k''nel. Kren''ef, T''doshok res luk rek grien forek res fel luraken.',
Text: 'Deploy on table.  Where you have two non-unique aliens present, draw one battle destiny if unable to otherwise and opponent''s total power is -3. While Bossk at a site, (except Audience Chamber), Trandoshans are power +1 and forfeit +2.  May deploy non-[Virtual Block 6] Molator from Reserve Deck; reshuffle.  (Immune to Alter.)',
